-melonJS
melonJS is a lightweight yet powerful HTML5 framework designed from the ground up to provide a true plugin-free 'write-once, run-everywhere' gaming platform. 
melonJS is an open-source project and supported by a community of enthusiasts.

-Features:

StandAlone library with no dependencies
Supported on almost every Browser
Lightweight implementation

-Building melonJs

Node.js JavaScript and npm package manager required
Grunt Task Manager

$ [sudo] npm install -g grunt-cli

$ cd melonJS
$ npm install
$ grunt
